# grapher_functions_smoke.numos — Phase 9F. Insert sin/cos/tan/ln/log in 5 slots,
# plot them all on one Graph, screenshot, exit. Proves transcendental functions
# insert + serialize + graph without hanging (tan asymptotes, ln/log domain).
# Warning-only (screenshot, no golden); NOT CI-gated.
log "functions: start"
wait 180
open_app Grapher
wait 40
key down
key enter
key y
key =
key sin
key x
key enter
wait 16
key down
key enter
key y
key =
key cos
key x
key enter
wait 16
key down
key enter
key y
key =
key tan
key x
key enter
wait 16
key down
key enter
key y
key =
key ln
key x
key enter
wait 16
key down
key enter
key y
key =
key log
key x
key enter
wait 40
key graph
wait 100
key ac
key 0
wait 150
screenshot out/grapher_functions_smoke.ppm
key home
wait 50
assert_app Menu
log "functions: PASS - sin/cos/tan/ln/log plotted, exited clean"
